### ============================================
### PATTERN TESTS - Create Shapes
### ============================================

### All clocks horizontal (3 o'clock position)
POST http://{{host}}:{{port}}/test
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

board=0&clock=0&angle_h=90&angle_m=90

### All clocks vertical (12 o'clock position)
POST http://{{host}}:{{port}}/test
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

board=0&clock=0&angle_h=0&angle_m=0

### All clocks diagonal
POST http://{{host}}:{{port}}/test
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

board=0&clock=0&angle_h=45&angle_m=225

### Reset to zero position
POST http://{{host}}:{{port}}/test
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

board=0&clock=0&angle_h=0&angle_m=0